<section class="vh-100">
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-6 text-black">


        <div
          class="d-flex align-items-center h-custom-2 px-5 ms-xl-4 mt-5 pt-5 pt-xl-0 mt-xl-n5"
        >

          <form
            class="homeform"
            id="login-form"
            method="POST"
            action="/user/login"
          >

            <h3 class="fw-normal mb-3 pb-3" style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Play
              More</h3>

            <p>This website will act as a booking system for playgrounds. It
              will also provide option to host a match if people want to play a
              particular sport together. In this website users can create a post
              of their event. They can select a particular sport which they are
              going to play/host. They can also write reviews on playgrounds
              which are already existing. The purpose of application is to allow
              users to find nearby events / matches which they would like to
              join. If they have a location, they can host the game to play.</p>
